<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.10">
<l>mikka vulakuka ṭōṟu mēvikkaṇ ṇaṉṟiru mūrtti</l>
<l>nakkapi rāṉō ṭayaṉu mintira ṉummutalāka</l>
<l>tokka vamarar kuḻāṅka ḷeṅkum parantaṉa toṇṭīr</l>
<l>okkat toḻukiṟṟi rākil kaliyuka moṉṟumil laiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Joining the sacred form of Kṛṣṇa in every worlds that increased,</l>
<l>with Aja and Indra along with the lord who smiled as the first</l>
<l>the throngs of gathered immortals spread everywhere. You devotees,</l>
<l>if you equally worship, there won’t be any Kaliyuga.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
